{"tid":387248,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【睇路呀】證監：海天能源股權高度集中","createTime":"2017-09-04T13:09:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T13:09:51.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"69fcec5b0fdeec182f0f67c2b9b4b868e4dcf01e","tid":387248,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T13:09:51.000Z","msg":"海天能源(8261)被證監會指股權高度集中。證監會最近曾就該公司之股權分佈進行查訊，查訊結果顯示該公司於上月24日，19名股東連同控股股東，合共持有相當 於該公司已發行股本總額之93.64%，意味已發行股份僅6.36%由其他投資者持有。<br />\n<br />\n海天能源指，鑑於股權高度集中於數目不多之股東，即使少量股份成交，該公司之股份價格亦可能大幅波動，股東及有意投資者於買賣該公司股份時務請審慎行事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57169502&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170904\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57169502%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170904&d=s5yiQQ%2BuaZIOOUWr9FXDmtZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=cea78e79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57169502%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170904&h=d0debb35\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57169502&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170904</a>"}]}